data.description: This beautiful home features 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths.  Master bath has garden tub, double sinks, separate shower.  The family room is spacious and open.  Kitchen is large with black appliances, lots of cabinets and opens to the family room and dining/breakfast area.  The home is very well maintained and immaculate.  The covered patio opens to a nice private back yard.  Front porch and landscaped yard.  Neighborhood pool, park, trails and pond. New Norman Elementary in Riverwalk soon to be open.
